quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  4,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  4,1,logo apne perwar-digaar se daro jis ne tum ko 1 shakhs se pedakiya ( yani awwal ) is se is ka jora banaya. phir un dono se kasrat se mard o aurat ( peda karkay roye zameen par ) phela diye. aur khuda se jis ke naam ko tum apni haajat Bar aarey ka zareya banatay ho daro aur ( qata muwadat ) Arham se ( bachcho ) kuch shak nahi ke khuda tumhe dekh raha hai
  4,2,aur yatimon ka maal ( jo tumhari tehweel mein ho ) un ke hawalay kardo aur un ke pakeeza ( aur umdah ) maal ko ( apne naaqis aur ) buray maal se nah badlo. aur nah un ka maal apne maal mein mila kar khao. ke yeh bara sakht gunah hai
  4,3,aur agar tum ko is baat ka khauf ho ke yateem larkiyon ke baray insaaf nah kar sako ge to un ke siwa jo aurtain tum ko pasand hon do do ya teen teen ya chaar chaar un se nikah karlo. aur agar is baat ka andesha ho ke ( sab aurton se ) yaksaa sulooq nah krsko ge to aik aurat ( kaafi hai ) ya londi jis ke tum maalik ho. is se tum be insafi se bach jao ge
  4,4,aur aurton ko un ke mohar khusi se day diya karo. haan agar woh apni khusi se is mein se kuch tum ko chore den to usay zouq shoq se kha lo
  4,5,aur be aqlon ko un ka maal jisay khuda ne tum logon ke liye sabab maeeshat banaya hai mat do ( haan ) is mein se un ko khelati aur p_hnate rahay aur un se maqool baatein kehte raho
  4,6,aur yatimon ko baaligh honay taq kaam kaaj mein masroof rakho phir ( baaligh honay par ) agar un mein aqal ki pukhtagi dekho to un ka maal un ke hawalay kardo aur is khauf se ke woh barray ho jaien ge ( yani barray ho kar tum se apna maal wapas le len ge ) is ko fuzool kharchi aur jaldi mein nah ura dena. jo shakhs aasooda haal ho is ko ( aisay maal se qatee tor par ) parhaiz rakhna chahiye aur jo be Maqdoor ho woh munhasib tor par ( yani baqadar khidmat ) kuch le le aur jab un ka maal un ke hawalay karne lagu to gawah karliya karo. aur haqeeqat mein to khuda hi ( gawah aur ) hisaab lainay wala kaafi hai
  4,7,jo maal maa baap aur rishta daar chore mrin thora ho ya bohat. is mein mardon ka bhi hissa hai aur aurton ka bhi yeh hissay ( khuda ke ) muqarrar kiye hue hain
  4,8,aur jab meeras ki taqseem ke waqt ( ghair waris ) rishta daar aur yateem aur mohtaaj ajayeen to un ko bhi is mein se kuch day diya karo. aur sheree kalami se paish aaya karo
  4,9,aur aisay logon ko darna chahiye jo ( aisi haalat mein hon ke ) apne baad nanhay nanhay bachay chore jayen aur un ko un ki nisbat khauf ho ( ke un ke marnay ke baad un bicharoon kakiya haal hoga ) pas chahiye ke yeh log khuda se dareen aur maqool baat kahin
  4,10,log yatimon ka maal najaaiz tor par khatay hain woh apne pait mein aag bhartay hain. aur dozakh mein daaley jayen ge
  4,11,"khuda tumhari aulaad ke baray mein tum ko irshad farmata hai ke aik larke ka hissa do larkiyon ke hissay ke barabar hai. aur agar aulaad maiyat sirf larkiyan hi hon ( yani do ya ) do se ziyada to kal trke mein un kado tahai. aur agar sirf aik larki ho to is ka hissa nisf. aur maiyat ke maa baap ka yani dono mein se har aik ka trke mein chhata hissa bashart e kay maiyat ke aulaad ho. aur agar aulaad nah ho aur sirf maa baap hi is ke waris hon to aik tahai maa ka hissa. aur agar maiyat ke bhai bhi hon to maa ka chhata hissa. ( aur yeh taqseem tarka maiyat ki ) wasiyat ( ki tameel ) ke baad jo is ne ki ho ya qarz ke ( ada honay ke baad jo is ke zimmay ho amal mein aeye gi ) tum ko maloom nahi ke tumahray baap dadaon aur beton poton mein se faiday ke lehaaz se kon tum se ziyada qareeb hai, yeh hissay khuda ke muqarrar kiye hue hain aur khuda sab kuch jan-nay wala aur hikmat wala hai"
  4,12,"aur jo maal tumhari aurtain chore mrin. agar un ke aulaad nah ho to is mein nisf hissa tumhara. aur agar aulaad ho to trke mein tumhara hissa chothai. ( lekin yeh taqseem ) wasiyat ( ki tameel ) ke baad jo unhon ne ki ho ya qarz ke ( ada honay ke baad jo un ke zimmay ho, ki jaye gi ) aur jo maal tum ( mard ) chore mrw. agar tumahray aulaad nah ho to tumhari aurton ka is mein choutha hissa. aur agar aulaad ho to un ka aathwan hissa ( yeh hissay ) tumhari wasiyat ( ki tameel ) ke baad jo tum ne ki ho aur ( adaye ) qarz ke ( baad taqseem kiye jayen ge ) aur agar aisay mard ya aurat ki meeras ho jis ke nah baap ho nah beta magar is ke bhai behan ho to un mein se har aik ka chhata hissa aur agar aik se ziyada hon to sab aik tahai mein shareek hon ge ( yeh hissay bhi adaye wasiyat o qarz bashart e kay un se maiyat ne kisi ka nuqsaan nahkiya ho ( taqseem kiye jayen ge ) yeh khuda ka farmaan hai. aur khuda nihayat ilm wala ( aur ) nihayat halm wala hai"
  4,13,( yeh tamam ehkaam ) khuda ki hade hain. aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke paighambar ki farmabardari kere ga khuda is ko bahishtoon mein daakhil kere ga jin mein nehrein beh rahi hain woh un mein hamesha rahen ge. aur yeh barri kamyabi hai
  4,14,aur jo khuda aur is ke rasool ki nafarmani kere ga aur is ki hado se nikal jaye ga is ko khuda dozakh mein daaley ga jahan woh hamesha rahay ga. aur is ko zillat ka azaab hoga
  4,15,musalmano tumhari aurton mein jo badkaari ka irtikaab kar bathain un par apne logon mein se chaar shakhson ki shahadat lau. agar woh ( un ki badkaari ki ) gawahi den to un aurton ko gharon mein band rakho yahan taq ke mout un ka kaam tamam kardey ya khuda un ke liye koi aur Sabeel ( peda ) kere
  4,16,aur jo do mard tum mein se badkaari karen to un ko aeza do. phir agar woh tauba karlen aur nekokaar ho jaien to un ka peecha chore do. be shak khuda tauba qubool karne wala ( aur ) meharban hai
  4,17,khuda inhen logon ki tauba qubool farmata hai jo nadani se buri harkat kar baithy hain. phir jald tauba qubool kar lete hain pas aisay logon par khuda meharbani karta hai. aur woh sab kuch jaanta ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  4,18,aur aisay logon ki tauba qubool nahi hoti jo ( saari Umar ) buray kaam karte hain. yahan taq ke jab un mein se kisi mout آaa maujood ho to is waqt kehnay lagey ke ab mein tauba karta hon aur nah un ki ( tauba qubool hoti hai ) jo kufar ki haalat mein mrin. aisay logon ke liye hum ne azaab alim tayyar kar rakha hai
  4,19,momino! tum ko jaaiz nahi ke zabardasti aurton ke waris ban jao. aur ( dekhna ) is niyat se ke jo kuch tum ne un ko diya hai is mein se kuch le lau inhen ( gharon mein ) mein mat rok rakhna haan agar woh khulay tor par badkaari ki murtakib hon ( to rokna munhasib nahi ) aur un ke sath achi terhan raho saho agar woh tum ko napasand hon to ajab nahi ke tum kisi cheez ko napasand karo aur khuda is mein bohat si bhalai peda kardey
  4,20,aur agar tum aik aurat ko chore kar doosri aurat karni chaho. aur pehli aurat ko bohat saal maal day chuke ho to is mein se kuch mat lena. bhala tum najaaiz tor par aur Sarih zulm se apna maal is se wapas le logay ?
  4,21,aur tum diya howa maal kionkar wapas le satke ho jab ke tum aik dosray ke sath sohbat kar chukay ho. aur woh tum se ehad wasiq bhi le chuki hai
  4,22,aur jin aurton se tumahray baap ne nikahkiya ho un nikah mat karna ( magar jahliat mein ) jo ho chuka (so ho chukaا ) yeh nihayat be hiyai aur ( khuda ki ) na khushi ki baat thi. aur bohat bura dastoor tha
  4,23,tum par tumhari maaen aur betiyan aur behnain aur phophyan aur khalaiyn aur bhtijyan aur bhanjyan aur woh maaen jinhon ne tum ko doodh pilaya ho aur razai behnain aur sasein haraam kar di gayi hain aur jin aurton se tum mubashrat kar chuke ho un ki larkiyan jinhein tum parwarish karte ( ho woh bhi tum par haraam hain ) haan agar un ke sath tum ne mubashrat nah ki ho to ( un ki larkiyon ke sath nikah kar lainay mein ) tum par kuch gunah nahi aur tumahray salbi beton ki aurtain bhi aur do behnoon ka akhatta karna bhi ( haraam hai ) magar jo ho chuka ( so ho chuka ) be shak khuda bakhsnay wala ( aur ) reham karne wala hai
  4,24,aur shohar wali aurtain bhi ( tum par haraam hain ) magar woh jo ( aseer ho kar londion ke tor par ) tumahray qabzay mein ajayeen ( yeh hukum ) khuda ne tum ko likh diya hai aur un ( muharmat ) ke siwa aur aurtain tum ko halal hain is terhan se ke maal kharch kar ke un se nikah karlo bashart e kay ( nikah se ) maqsood Iffat qaim rakhna ho nah shehwat rani to jin aurton se tum faida haasil karo un ka mohar jo muqarrarkiya ho ada kardo aur agar muqarrar karne ke baad aapas ki razamandi se mohar mein kami Beshi karlo to tum par kuch gunah nahi be shak khuda sab kuch jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  4,25,aur jo shakhs tum mein se momin azad aurton ( yani بیبیوں ) se nikah karne ka Maqdoor nah rakhay to momin londion mein hi jo tumahray qabzay mein aagai hon ( nikah karle ) aur khuda tumahray imaan ko achi terhan jaanta hai tum aapas mein aik dosray ke hum jins ho to un londion ke sath un ke malikon se ijazat haasil karkay nikah kar lau aur dastoor ke mutabiq un ka mohar bhi ada kardo bashart e kay Afifa hon nah aisi ke khullam khula badkaari karen aur nah darparda dosti karna chahain phir agar nikah mein aakar badkaari ka irtikaab kar bathain to jo saza azad aurton ( yani bibiyon ) ke liye hai is ki aadhi un ko ( di jaye ) yeh ( londi ke sath nikah karne ki ) ijazat is shakhs ko hai jisay gunah kar bethnay ka andesha ho aur agar sabr karo to yeh tumahray liye bohat acha hai aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  4,26,khuda chahta hai ke ( apni ayatain ) tum se khol khol kar bayan farmaiye aur tum ko aglay logon ke tareeqay betaye aur tum par meharbani kere aur khuda jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  4,27,aur khuda to chahta hai ke tum par meharbani kere aur jo log apni khawahishon ke peechay chaltay hain woh chahtay hain ke tum seedhay rastay se bhatak kar daur ja parro
  4,28,khuda chahta hai ke tum par se boojh halka kere aur ensaan ( tbaan ) kamzor peda howa hai
  4,29,momino! aik dosray ka maal na-haq nah khao haan agar aapas ki razamandi se tijarat ka lain deen ho ( aur is se maali faida haasil ho jaye to woh jaaiz hai ) aur apne aap ko halaak nah karo kuch shak nahi ke khuda tum par meharban hai
  4,30,aur jo ta-adi aur zulm se aisa kere ga hum is ko anqareeb jahannum mein daakhil karen ge aur yeh khuda ko aasaan hai
  4,31,agar tum barray barray gunaaho se jin se tum ko manakiya jata hai ijtinab rakho ge to hum tumahray ( chhootey chhootey ) gunah maaf kar dein ge aur tumhe izzat ke makanon mein daakhil karen ge
  4,32,aur jis cheez mein khuda ne tum mein se baaz ko baaz par fazeelat di hai is ki hawas mat karo mardon ko un kamon ka sawab hai jo unhon ne kiye aur aurton ko un kamon ka sawab hai jo unhon ne kiye aur khuda se is ka fazl ( vkrm ) mangte raho kuch shak nahi ke khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
  4,33,aur jo maal maa baap aur rishta daar chore mrin to ( haq daaron mein taqseem kardo ke ) hum ne har aik ke haqdaar muqarrar kardiye hain aur jin logon se tum ehad kar chukay ho un ko bhi un ka hissa do be shak khuda har cheez ke samnay hai
  4,34,mard aurton par musallat aur hakim hain is liye ke khuda ne baaz ko baaz se afizal banaya hai aur is liye bhi ke mard apna maal kharch karte hain to jo naik bibiyanhain woh mardon ke hukum par chalti hain aur un ke peeth peechay khuda ki hifazat mein ( maal vaabro ki ) khabardari karti hain aur jin aurton ki nisbat tumhe maloom ho ke sar kashi ( aur bud khoi ) karne lagi hain to ( pehlay ) un ko ( zabani ) samjhao ( agar nah samjhain to ) phir un ke sath sona tark kardo agar is par bhi baz nah ayen to zdokob karo aur agar farmanbardar ho jaien to phir un ko aeza dainay ka koi bahana mat dhuundo be shak khuda sab se aala ( aur ) jallel al-qadar hai
  4,35,aur agar tum ko maloom ho ke miyan biwi mein un ban hai to aik munhsif mard ke khandan mein se aur aik munhsif aurat ke khandan mein se muqarrar karo woh agar sulah kara dainee chahain ge to khuda un mein muwafiqat peda kardey ga kuch shak nahi ke khuda sab kuch jaanta aur sab baton se khabardaar hai
  4,36,aur khuda hi ki ibadat karo aur is ke sath kisi cheez ko shareek nah banaao aur maa baap aur qaraabat walon aur yatimon aur mohtajon aur rishta daar humsaiyon aur ajnabi humsaiyon aur rfqaye pehlu ( yani paas bethnay walon ) aur musafiron aur jo log tumahray qabzay mein hon sab ke sath ahsaan karo ke khuda ( ahsaan karne walon ko dost rakhta hai aur ) taqqabur karne walay barayi maarny walay ko dost nahi rakhta
  4,37,jo khud bhi bukhal karen aur logon ko bhi bukhal skhayin aur jo ( maal ) khuda ne un ko apne fazl se ataa farmaya hai usay chhupa chhupa ke rakhen aur hum ne nashukron ke liye zillat ka azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  4,38,aur kharch bhi karen to ( khuda ke liye nahi balkay ) logon ke dikhaane ko aur imaan nah khuda par layein aur nah roz akhirat par ( aisay logon ko saathi shetan hai ) aur jis ka saathi shetan howa to ( kuch shak nahi ke ) woh bura saathi hai
  4,39,aur agar yeh log khuda par aur roz qayamat par imaan laatay aur jo kuch khuda ne un ko diya tha is mein se kharch karte to un kakiya nuqsaan hota aur khuda un ko khoob jaanta hai
  4,40,khuda kisi ki zara bhi haq talfi nahi karta aur agar neki ( ki ) hogi to is ko dochnd kardey ga aur apne haan se ajre azeem bakhshay ga
  4,41,bhala is din kakiya haal hoga jab hum har ummat mein se ahwaal betaye walay ko bulayen ge aur tum ko un logon ka haal ( bitanay ko ) gawah talab karen ge
  4,42,is roz kafir aur paighambar ke nafarman arzoo karen ge ke kash un ko zameen mein madfoon karkay matti barabar kar di jati aur khuda se koi baat chhupa nahi saken ge
  4,43,momino! jab tum nashay ki haalat mein ho to jab taq ( un alfaaz ko ) jo munh se kaho samajhney ( nah ) lagu namaz ke paas nah jao aur janabat ki haalat mein bhi ( namaz ke paas nah jao ) jab taq ke ghusal ( nah ) karlo haan agar bhalt safar raste chalay jarahay ho aur pani nah milnay ke sabab ghusal nah krsko to tayamum karkay namaz parh lau ) aur agar tum bemaar ho safar mein ho ya tum mein se koi beeet al khala se ho kar aaya ho ya tum aurton se hum bistar hue ho aur tumhe pani nah miley to pak matti lau aur munh aur hathon par maseh ( karkay tayamum ) karlo be shak khuda maaf karne wala aur bakhsnay wala hai
  4,44,bhala tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jin ko kitaab se hissa diya gaya tha ke woh gumraahi ko khridte hain aur chahtay hain ke tum bhi raste se bhatak jao
  4,45,aur khuda tumahray dushmanon se khoob waaqif hai aur khuda hi kaafi karsaaz hai aur kaafi madadgaar hai
  4,46,aur yeh jo yahodi hain un mein se kuch log aisay bhi hain ke kalmaat ko un ke maqamat se badal dete hain aur kehte hain ke hum ne sun liya aur nahi maana aur sniye nah snwaye jao aur zabaan ko maror kar aur deen mein ta'an ki raah se ( tum se guftagu ) ke waqt ra-ana kehte hain aur agar ( yun ) kehte hain ke hum ne sun liya aur maan liya aur ( sirf ) asmaa aur ( raa'inaa ki jagah ) anzurnaa ( kehte ) to un ke haq mein behtar hota aur baat bhi bohat durust hoti lekin Khuda ne un ke kufar ke sabab un par laanat kar rakhi hai to yeh kuch thoray hi imaan laatay hain
  4,47,ae kitaab walo! qabal is ke ke hum logon ke monhon ko bigaar kar un ki peeth ki taraf phair den ya un par is terhan laanat karen jis terhan haftay walon par ki thi hamari nazil ki hui kitaab par jo tumhari kitaab ki bhi tasdeeq karti hai imaan le aao aur khuda ne jo hukum farmaya so ( samajh lau ke ) hochuka
  4,48,khuda is gunah ko nahi bakhshay ga ke kisi ko is ka shareek banaya jaye aur is ke siwa aur gunah jis ko chahay maaf kardey aur jis ne khuda ka shareek muqarrarkiya is ne bara bohtan baandha
  4,49,kiya tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jo apne tain pakeeza kehte hain ( nahi ) balkay khuda hi jis ko chahta hai pakeeza karta hai aur un par dhaagay ke barabar bhi zulm nahi hoga
  4,50,dekho yeh khuda par kaisa jhoot ( tufaan ) bandhtay hain aur yahi gunah Sarih kaafi hai
  4,51,bhala tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jin ko kitaab se hissa diya gaya hai ke buton aur shetan ko mantay hain aur kufar ke baray mein kehte hain ke yeh log mominon ki nisbat seedhay raste par hain
  4,52,yahi log hain jin par khuda ne laanat ki hai aur jis par khuda laanat kere to tum is ka kisi ko madadgaar nah pao ge
  4,53,kiya un ke paas badshahi ka kuch hissa hai to logon ko tall barabar bhi nah den ge
  4,54,ya jo khuda ne logon ko apne fazl se day rakha hai is ka hasad karte hain to hum ne khandan ibrahim ko kitaab aur danai ataa farmai thi aur saltanat azeem bhi bakhsh thi
  4,55,phir logon mein se kisi ne to is kitaab ko maana aur koi is se ruka ( aur hata ) raha to nah maan-ne walon ( ke jalanay ) ko dozakh ki jalti hui aag kaafi hai
  4,56,jin logon ne hamari ayaton se kufarkiya un ko hum anqareeb aag mein daakhil karen ge jab un ki khalen Gul ( aur jal ) jayen gi to hum aur khalen badal den ge taakay ( hamesha ) azaab ( ka maza chahkte ) rahen be shak khuda ghalib hikmat wala hai
  4,57,aur jo imaan laaye aur naik amal karte rahay un ko hum bahishtoon mein daakhil karen ge jin ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hain woh un mein hamesha hamesha rahen ge wahan un ke liye pak bibiyanhain aur un ko hum ghany saaye mein daakhil karen ge
  4,58,khuda tum ko hukum deta hai ke amanat walon ki amanatain un ke hawalay kardiya karo aur jab logon mein faisla karne lagu to insaaf se faislakiya karo khuda tumhe bohat khoob nasiyaat karta hai be shak khuda santa aur daikhta hai
  4,59,momino! khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmabardari karo aur jo tum mein se sahib hukoomat hain un ki bhi aur agar kisi baat mein tum mein ikhtilaaf waqay ho to agar khuda aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhtay ho to is mein khuda aur is ke rasool ( ke hukum ) ki taraf rujoo karo yeh bohat achi baat hai aur is ka maal bhi acha hai
  4,60,kiya tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jo daawa to yeh karte hain ke jo ( kitaab ) tum par nazil hui aur jo ( kitaaben ) tum se pehlay nazil huien un sab par imaan rakhtay hain aur chahtay yeh hain ke apna muqadma aik sarkash ke paas le ja kar faisla karayen halaank un ko hukum diya gaya tha ke is se aitqaad nah rakhen aur shetan ( to yeh ) chahta hai ke un ko b_hka kar raste se daur daal day
  4,61,aur jab un se kaha jata hai ke jo hukum khuda ne nazil farmaya hai is ki taraf ( rujoo karo ) aur paighambar ki taraf aao to tum munhafiqon ko dekhte ho ke tum se aaraaz karte aur ruke jatay hain
  4,62,to kaisi ( nedamat ki ) baat hai ke jab un ke aamaal ( ki shamat se ) un par koi museebat waqay hoti hai to tumahray paas bhage atay hain aur kasmain khatay hain ke wallah hamara maqsood to bhalai aur muwafiqat tha
  4,63,un logon ke dilon mein jo kuch hai khuda is ko khoob jaanta hai tum un ( ki baton ) ko kuch khayaal nah karo aur inhen nasiyaat karo aur un se aisi baatein kaho jo un ke dilon mein assar kar jayen
  4,64,aur hum ne jo paighambar bheja hai is liye bheja hai ke khuda ke farmaan ke mutabiq is ka hukum maana jaye aur yeh log jab apne haq mein zulm kar baithy they agar tumahray paas atay aur khuda se bakhshish mangte aur rasool ( khuda ) bhi un ke liye bakhshish talab karte to khuda ko maaf karne wala ( aur ) meharban paate
  4,65,tumahray perwar-digaar ki qasam yeh log jab taq apne tanazeaat mein tumhe munhsif nah banayen aur jo faisla tum kardo is se apne dil mein tang nah hon balkay is ko khusi se maan len tab taq momin nahi hon ge
  4,66,aur agar hum inhen hukum dete ke apne aap ko qatal kar daalo ya apne ghar chore kar nikal jao to un mein se thoray hi aisa karte aur agar yeh is nasiyaat par karband hotay jo un ko ki jati hai to un ke haq mein behtar aur ( deen mein ) ziyada saabit qadmi ka mojab hota
  4,67,aur hum un ko apne haan se ajar azeem bhi ataa farmatay
  4,68,aur seedha rasta bhi dikhata
  4,69,aur jo log khuda aur is ke rasool ki itaat karte hain woh ( qayamat ke roz ) un logon ke sath hon ge jin par khuda ne bara fazlkiya yani anbia aur Seddiq aur shaheed aur naik log aur un logon ki rafaqat bohat hi khoob hai
  4,70,yeh khuda ka fazl hai aur khuda jan-nay wala kaafi hai
  4,71,momino! ( jehaad ke liye ) hathyaar le liya karo phir ya to jamaat jamaat ho kar nikla karo ya sab ikhatay coachkiya karo
  4,72,aur tum mein koi aisa bhi hai ke ( amdan ) der lagaata hai. phir agar tum par koi museebat par jaye to kehta hai ke khuda ne mujh par barri meharbani ki ke mein un mein mojood nah tha
  4,73,aur agar khuda tum par fazl kere to is terhan se ke goya tum mein is mein dosti thi hi nahi ( ke afsos karta aur ) kehta hai ke kash mein bhi un ke sath hota to maqsad azeem haasil karta
  4,74,to jo log akhirat ( ko khridte aur is ) ke badlay duniya ki zindagi ko bechna chahtay hain unn ko chahiye ke khuda ki raah mein jung karen aur jo shakhs khuda ki raah mein jung kere aur shaheed hojaye ya ghalba paye hum anqareeb is ko bara sawab den ge
  4,75,aur tum kokiya howa hai ke khuda ki raah mein aur unn be bas mardon aur aurton aur bachon ki khatir nahi lartay jo duayenkiya karte hain ke ae perwar-digaar hum ko is shehar se jis ke rehne walay zalim hain nikaal kar kahin aur le ja. aur apni taraf se kisi ko hamara haami bana. aur apni hi taraf se kisi ko hamara madadgaar muqarrar farma
  4,76,jo momin hain woh to khuda ke liye lartay hain aur jo kafir hain woh buton ke liye lartay hain so tum shetan ke mddgaron se laro. ( aur daro mat ) kyunkay shetan ka dao boda hota hai
  4,77,bhala tum ne un logon ko nahi dekha jin ko ( pehlay yeh ) hukum diya gaya tha ke apne hathon ko ( jung se ) rokay raho aur namaz parhte raho aur zakaat dete raho phir jab un par jehaad farz kardiya gaya to baaz log un mein se logon se yun darny lagey jaisay khuda se dara karte hain balkay is se bhi ziyada aur barbaranay lagey ke ae khuda to ne hum par jehaad ( jald ) kyun farz kardiya thori muddat aur hamein kyun mohlat nah di ( ae paighambar un seen ) y keh do ke duniya ka faida bohat thora hai aur bohat achi cheez to parhaizgaar ke liye ( nijaat ) akhirat hai aur tum par dhaagay barabar bhi zulm nahikiya jaye ga
  4,78,( ae jehaad se darny walo ) tum kahin raho mout to tumhe aa kar rahay gi khuwa barray barray mehloon mein raho aur un logon ko agar koi faida pohanchana hai to kehte hain yeh khuda ki taraf se hai aur agar koi gznd pohanchana hai to ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam tum se ) kehte hain ke yeh gznd aap ki wajah se ( hamein pouncha ) hai keh do ke ( ranj o rahat ) sab allah hi ki taraf se hai un logon kokiya hogaya hai ke baat bhi nahi samajh satke
  4,79,ae ( aadam zaad ) tujh ko jo faida puhanche woh khuda ki taraf se hai aur jo nuqsaan puhanche woh teri hi ( shamat aamaal ) ki wajah se hai aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tum ko logon ( ki hadaayat ) ke liye paighambar bana kar bheja hai aur ( is baat ka ) khuda hi gawah kaafi hai
  4,80,jo shakhs rasool ki farmabardari kere ga to be shak is ne khuda ki farmabardari ki aur jo nafarmani kere ga to ae paighambar tumhe hum ne un ka nigehbaan bana kar nahi bheja
  4,81,aur yeh log munh se to kehte hain ke ( aap ki ) farmabardari ( dil se Manzoor hai ) lekin jab tumahray paas se chalay jatay hain to un mein se baaz log raat ko tumhari baton ke khilaaf mashwaray karte hain aur jo mashwaray yeh karte hain khuda un ko likh laita hai to un ka kuch khayaal nah karo aur khuda par bharosa rakho aur khuda hi kaafi karsaaz hai
  4,82,bhala yeh quran mein ghhor kyun nahi karte? agar yeh khuda ke siwa kisi aur ka ( kalaam ) hota to is mein ( bohat sa ) ikhtilaaf paate
  4,83,aur jab un ke paas aman ya khauf ki koi khabar pahunchti hai to is ko mashhoor kardete hain aur agar is ko paighambar aur apne sardaro ke paas pohanchate to tahaqeeq karne walay is ki tahaqeeq kar letay aur agar tum par khuda ka fazl aur is ki meharbani nah hoti to chand ashkhaas ke siwa sab shetan ke pairo ho jatay
  4,84,to ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum khuda ki raah mein laro tum apne siwa kisi ke zimma daar nahi aur mominon ko bhi targheeb do qareeb hai ke khuda kafiroon ki larai ko band kardey aur khuda larai ke aitbaar se bohat sakht hai aur saza ke lehaaz se bhi bohat sakht hai
  4,85,jo shakhs naik baat ki sifarish kere to is ko is ( ke sawab ) mein se hissa miley ga aur jo buri baat ki sifarish kere is ko is ( ke azaab ) mein se hissa miley ga aur khuda har cheez par qudrat rakhta hai
  4,86,aur jab tum ko koi dua day to ( jawab mein ) tum is se behtar ( kalme ) se ( usay ) dua do ya inhen lafzon se dua do be shak khuda har cheez ka hisaab lainay wala hai
  4,87,khuda ( woh mabood barhaq hai ke ) is ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi woh qayamat ke din tum sab ko zaroor jama kere ga aur khuda se barh kar baat ka sacha kon hai ?
  4,88,tokiya sabab hai ke tum munhafiqon ke baray mein do giroh ho rahay ho halaank khuda ne un ko un ke krtoton ke sabab ondha kardiya haikiya tum chahtay ho ke jis shakhs ko khuda ne gumraah kardiya hai is ko raste par le aao aur jis shakhs ko khuda gumraah kardey to is ke liye kabhi bhi rasta nahi pao ge
  4,89,woh to yahi chahtay hain ke jis terhan woh khud kafir hain ( isi terhan ) tum bhi kafir ho kar ( sab ) barabar hojao to jab taq woh khuda ki raah mein watan nah chore jayen un mein se kisi ko dost nah banana agar ( tark watan ko ) qubool nah karen to un ko pakar lau aur jahan pao qatal kardo aur un mein se kisi ko apna Rafeeq aur madadgaar nah banaao
  4,90,magar jo log aisay logon se ja miley hon jin mein aur tum mein ( sulah ka ) ehad ho ya is haal mein ke un ke dil tumahray sath ya apni qoum ke sath larnay se ruk gay hon tumahray paas ajayeen ( to Ihtiraz zurori nahi ) aur agar khuda chahta to un ko tum par ghalib kardaita to woh tum se zaroor lartay phir agar woh tum se ( jung karne se ) kinara kashi karen aur laren nahi aur tumhari taraf sulah ( ka pegham ) bhejen to khuda ne tumahray liye un par ( zabardasti karne ki ) koi Sabeel muqarrar nahi ki
  4,91,tum kuch aur log aisay bhi pao ge jo yeh chahtay hain ke tum se bhi aman mein rahen aur apni qoum se bhi aman mein rahen lekin fitnah angazi ko bulaye jayen to is mein avndhe munh gir parrin to aisay log agar tum se ( larnay se ) kinara kashi nah karen aur nah tumhari taraf ( pegham ) sulah bhejen aur nah apne hathon ko rokain to un ko pakar lau aur jahan pao qatal kardo un logon ke muqablay mein hum ne tumahray liye sanad Sarih muqarrar kar di hai
  4,92,aur kisi momin ko Shayan nahi ke momin ko maar daaley magar bhool kar aur jo bhool kar bhi momin ko maar daaley to ( aik to ) aik musalman ghulam azad kardey aur ( dosray ) maqtool ke varson ko khoon baha day haan agar woh maaf kar dein ( to un ko ikhtiyar hai ) agar maqtool tumahray dushmanon ki jamaat mein se ho aur woh khud momin ho to sirf aik musalman ghulam azad karna chahiye aur agar maqtool aisay logon mein se ho jin mein aur tum mein sulah ka ehad ho to warsaan maqtool ko khoon baha dena aur aik musalman ghulam azad karna chahiye aur jis ko yeh muyassar nah ho woh mutawatar do mahinay ke rozay rakhay yeh ( kaffara ) khuda ki taraf se ( qubool ) tauba ( ke liye ) hai aur khuda ( sab kuch ) jaanta aur barri hikmat wala hai
  4,93,aur jo shakhs musalman ko qasdan maar daaley ga to is ki saza dozakh hai jis mein woh hamesha ( jalta ) rahay ga aur khuda is par ghazabnak hoga aur is par laanat kere ga aur aisay shakhs ke liye is ne bara ( sakht ) azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  4,94,momino! jab tum khuda ki raah mein bahar niklo karo to tahaqeeq se kaam liya karo aur jo shakhs tum se salam alik kere is se yeh nah kaho ke tum momin nahi aur is se tumhari gharz yeh ho ke duniya ki zindagi ka faida haasil karo so khuda ke nazdeek bohat se ghanimatainhain tum bhi to pehlay aisay hi they phir khuda ne tum par ahsaankiya to ( aindah ) tahaqeeq karliya karo aur jo amal tum karte ho khuda ko sab ki khabar hai
  4,95,jo musalman ( gharon mein ) baith rehtay ( aur larnay se jee churatay ) hain aur koi izr nahi rakhtay woh aur jo khuda ki raah mein apne maal aur jaan se lartay hain woh dono barabar nahi ho satke khuda ne maal aur jaan se jehaad karne walon ko baith rehne walon par darjay mein fazeelat bakhsh hai aur ( go ) naik wada sab se hai lekin ajar azeem ke lehaaz se khuda ne jehaad karne walon ko baith rehne walon par kahin fazeelat bakhsh hai
  4,96,( yani ) khuda ki taraf se darjaat mein aur bakhshish mein aur rehmat mein aur khuda bara bakhsnay wala ( aur ) meharban hai
  4,97,aur jo log apni jaanun par zulm karte hain jab farishtay un ki jaan qabz karne lagtay hain to un se puchhte hain ke tum kis haal mein they woh kehte hain ke hum malik mein aajiz o natawan they farishtay kehte hainkiya khuda ka malik farakh nahi tha ke tum is mein hijrat kar jatay aisay logon ka thikana dozakh hai aur woh buri jagah hai
  4,98,haan jo mard aur aurtain aur bachay be bas hain ke nah to koi charah kar satke hain aur nah rasta jantay hain
  4,99,qareeb hai ke khuda aison ko maaf kardey aur khuda maaf karne wala ( aur ) bakhsnay wala hai
  4,100,aur jo shakhs khuda ki raah mein ghar baar chore jaye woh zameen mein bohat si jagah aur kashaish paye ga aur jo shakhs khuda aur rasool ki taraf hijrat karkay ghar se nikal jaye phir is ko mout a pakray to is ka sawab khuda ke zimmay hochuka aur khuda bakhsnay wala aur meharban hai
  4,101,aur jab tum safar ko jao to tum par kuch gunah nahi ke namaz ko kam karkay parho bashart e kay tum ko khauf ho ke kafir log tum ko aeza den ge be shak kafir tumahray khulay dushman hain
  4,102,aur ( ae paighambar ) jab tum un ( mujahideen ke lashkar ) mein ho aur un ko namaz parhanay lagu to chahiye ke un ki aik jamaat tumahray sath musallah ho kar khari rahay jab woh sajda karchukay to paray ho jayen phir doosri jamaat jis ne namaz nahi parhi ( un ki jagah ) aeye aur hooshiyar aur musallah ho kar tumahray sath namaz ada kere kafir is ghaat mein hain ke tum zara apne hathyaaron aur samaan se ghaafil ho jao to tum par yakbargi hamla kar dein agar tum barish ke sabab takleef mein ya bemaar ho to tum par kuch gunah nahi ke hathyaar utaar rakho magar hooshiyar zaroor rehna khuda ne kafiroon ke liye zillat ka azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  4,103,phir jab tum namaz tamam kar chuko to kharray aur baithy aur letey ( har haalat mein ) khuda ko yaad karo phir jab khauf jata rahay to ( is terhan se ) namaz parho ( jis terhan aman ki haalat mein parhte ho ) be shak namaz ka mominon par auqaat ( muqarara ) mein ada karna farz hai
  4,104,aur kufar ka peecha karne mein susti nah karna agar tum be aaraam hotay ho to jis terhan tum be aaraam hotay ho isi terhan woh bhi be aaraam hotay hain aur tum khuda se aisi aisi umeeden rakhtay ho jo woh nahi rakh satke aur khuda sab kuch jaanta aur ( barri ) hikmat wala hai
  4,105,( ae paighambar ) hum ne tum par sachhi kitaab nazil ki hai taakay khuda ki hadaayat ke mutabiq logon ke muqadmaat mein faisla karo aur ( dekho ) dagha -bazon ki himayat mein kabhi behas nah karna
  4,106,aur khuda se bakhshish maangna be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  4,107,aur log apne hum jnson ki khayanat karte hain un ki taraf se behas nah karna kyunkay khuda khaa-in aur murtakib juraim ko dost nahi rakhta
  4,108,yeh logon se to chaptay hain aur khuda se nahi chaptay halaank jab woh raton ko aisi baton ke mashwaraykiya karte hain jin ko woh pasand nahi karta un ke sath howa karta hai aur khuda un ke ( tamam ) kamon par ihata kiye hue hai
  4,109,bhala tum log duniya ki zindagi mein to un ki taraf se behas kar letay ho qayamat ko un ki taraf se khuda ke sath kon jhagrre ga aur kon un ka wakeel banay ga ?
  4,110,aur jo shakhs koi bura kaam kar baithy ya apne haq mein zulm karle phir khuda se bakhshish mangay to khuda ko bakhsnay wala aur meharban paye ga
  4,111,aur jo koi gunah karta hai to is ka wabaal isi par hai aur khuda jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  4,112,aur jo shakhs koi qasoor ya gunah to khud kere lekin is se kisi be gunah ko mohtamim kardey to is ne bohtan aur Sarih gunah ka boojh apne sir par rakha
  4,113,aur agar tum par khuda ka fazl aur meharbani nah hoti to un mein se aik jamaat tum ko behkanay ka qasad kar hi chuki thi aur yeh apne siwa ( kisi ko ) b_hka nahi satke aur nah tumhara kuch bigaar satke hain aur khuda ne tum par kitaab aur danai nazil farmai hai aur tumhe woh baatein sikhayi hain jo tum jantay nahi they aur tum par khuda ka bara fazl hai
  4,114,un logon ki bohat si mushwaratain achi nahi hain ( is shakhs ki mashwarat achi hosakti hai ) jo khairaat ya naik baat ya logon mein sulah karne ko kahe aur jo aisay kaam khuda ki khushnodi haasil karne ke liye kere ga to hum is ko bara sawab dain ge
  4,115,aur jo shakhs seedha rasta maloom honay ke baad paighambar ki mukhalif kere aur mominon ke raste ke siwa aur raste par chalay to jidhar woh chalta hai hum usay idhar hi chalne den ge aur ( qayamat ke din ) jahannum mein daakhil karen ge aur woh buri jagah hai
  4,116,khuda is ke gunah ko nahi bakhshay ga ke kisi ko is ka shareek banaya jaye aur is ke siwa ( aur gunah ) jis ko chahiye ga bakhash day ga. aur jis ne khuda ke sath shareek banaya woh raste se daur ja para
  4,117,yeh jo khuda ke siwa parastish karte hain to aurton ki aur pkarte hain to shetan ki sarkash hi ko
  4,118,jis par khuda ne laanat ki hai ( jo khuda se ) kehnay laga mein tairay bundon se ( ghair khuda ki Nazar dlwa kar maal ka ) aik muqarrar hissa le liya karoon ga .
  4,119,aur un ko gumraah karta aur umeeden dilaata rahon ga aur yeh sakata rahon ga ke janwaron ke kaan cheertay rahen aur ( yeh bhi ) kehta rahon ga ke woh khuda ki banai hui sooraton ko bdalty rahen aur jis shakhs ne khuda ko chore kar shetan ko dost banaya aur woh Sarih nuqsaan mein par gaya
  4,120,woh un ko waday deta raha aur umeeden dilaata hai aur jo kuch shetan inhen waday deta hai jo dhoka hi dhoka hai
  4,121,aisay logon ka thikana jahannum hai. aur woh wahan se mukhlasi nahi paskin ge
  4,122,aur jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay un ko hum bahishtoon mein daakhil karen ge jin ke neechay nehrein jari hain. Abdul -aabaad un mein rahen ge. yeh khuda ka sacha wada hai. aur khuda se ziyada baat ka sacha kon ho sakta hai
  4,123,( nijaat ) nah to tumhari aarzouon par hai aur nah ahal kitaab ki aarzouon par. jo shakhs buray amal kere ga usay isi ( terhan ) ka badla diya jaye ga aur woh khuda ke siwa nah kisi ko himayati paye ga aur nah madadgaar
  4,124,aur jo naik kaam kere ga mard ho ya aurat aur woh sahib imaan bhi hoga to aisay log bahisht mein daakhil hon ge aur un ki tall barabar bhi haq talfi nah ki jaye gi
  4,125,aur is shakhs se kis ka deen acha ho sakta hai jis ne hukum khuda ko quboolkiya aur woh nekokaar bhi hai. aur ibrahim ke deen ka pairo hai jo yaksoo( musalman ) they aur khuda ne ibrahim ko apna dost banaya tha
  4,126,aur aasman o zameen mein jo kuch hai sab khuda hi ka hai. aur khuda har cheez par ihatay kiye hue hai
  4,127,( ae paighambar ) log tum se ( yateem ) aurton ke baray mein Fatwa talab karte hain. keh do ke khuda tum ko un ke ( sath nikah karne ke ) muamlay mein ijazat deta hai aur jo hukum is kitaab mein pehlay diya gaya hai woh un yateem aurton ke baray mein hai jin ko tum un ka haq to dete nahi aur khwahish rakhtay ho ke un ke sath nikah karlo aur ( neez ) becharay bacchus bachon ke baray mein. aur yeh ( bhi hukum deta hai ) ke yatimon ke baray mein insaaf par qaim raho. aur jo bhalai tum karo ge khuda is ko jaanta hai
  4,128,aur agar kisi aurat ko apne khawand ki taraf se zayad-ti ya be raghbati ka andesha ho tum miyan biwi par kuch gunah nahi ke aapas mein kisi qarardad par sulah karlen. aur sulah khoob ( cheez ) hai aur tabiyatain to bukhal ki taraf mael hoti hain aur agar tum نneko kariaur parhaiz gari karo ge to khuda tumahray sab kamon se waaqif hai
  4,129,aur tum khua kitna hi chaho aurton mein hargiz barabari nahi krsko ge to aisa bhi nah karna ke aik hi ki taraf dhal jao aur doosri ko ( aisi haalat mein ) chore do ke goya idhar howa mein latak rahi hai aur agar aapas mein muwafiqat karlo aur parhaiz gari karo to khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  4,130,aur agar miyan biwi ( mein muwafiqat nah hosakay aur ) aik dosray se judda ho jaien to khuda har aik ko apni doulat se ghanni kardey ga aur khuda barri kashaish wala aur hikmat wala hai
  4,131,aur jo kuch asmano aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab khuda hi ka hai. aur jin logon ko tum se pehlay kitaab di gayi thi un ko bhi aur ( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) tum ko bhi hum ne hukum takeedikiya hai ke khuda se drtay raho aur agar kufar karo ge to ( samajh rakho ke ) jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab khuda hi ka hai. aur khuda be parwa aur sazawar hamdo sana hai
  4,132,aur ( phir sun rakho ke ) jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab khuda hi ka hai aur khuda karsaaz kaafi hai
  4,133,logo! agar woh chahay to tum ko fanaa kardey aur ( tumhari jagah ) aur logon ko peda kardey. aur khuda is baat par Qadir hai
  4,134,jo shakhs duniya ( mein amlon ) ki jaza ka taalib ho to khuda ke paas duniya aur akhirat ( dono ) ke liye ajar ( mojood ) hain. aur khuda santa daikhta hai
  4,135,ae imaan walo! insaaf par qaim raho aur khuda ke liye sachhi gawahi do khuwa ( is mein ) tumhara ya tumahray maa baap aur rishta daaron ka nuqsaan hi ho. agar koi Ameer hai ya faqeer to khuda un ka kher khuwa hai. to tum khwahish nafs ke peechay chal kar Adal ko nah chore dena. agar tum pecheeda shahadat do ge ya ( shahadat se ) bachna chaho ge to ( jaan rakho ) khuda tumahray sab kamon se waaqif hai
  4,136,momino! khuda par aur is ke rasool par aur jo kitaab is ne apni paighambar ( aakhir uz zamaan ) par nazil ki hai aur jo kitaaben is se pehlay nazil ki theen sab par imaan lao. aur jo shakhs khuda aur is ke firshton aur is ki kitabon aur is ke payghambaroon aur roz-e-qayamat se inkaar kere woh raste se bhatak kar daur ja para
  4,137,jo log imaan laaye phir kafir hogaye phir imaan laaye phir kafir hogaye phir kufar mein barhatay gay un ko khuda nah to bakhshay ga aur nah seedha rasta dukhaay ga
  4,138,( ae paighambar ) munhafiqon ( yani do rkhe logon ) ko basharat سناد do ke un ke liye dukh dainay wala azaab ( tayyar ) hai
  4,139,jo mominon ko chore kar kafiroon ko dost banatay hain.kiya yeh un ke haan izzat haasil karna chahtay hain to izzat to sab khuda hi ki hai
  4,140,aur khuda ne tum ( mominon ) par apni kitaab mein ( yeh hukum ) nazil farmaya hai ke jab tum ( kahin ) suno ke khuda ki ayaton se inkaar ho raha hai aur un ki hansi udai jati hai to jab taq woh log aur baatein ( nah ) karne lagen. un ke paas mat betho. warna tum bhi inhen jaisay hojao ge. kuch shak nahi ke khuda munhafiqon aur kafiroon sab ko dozakh mein akatha karne wala hai
  4,141,jo tum ko dekhte rehtay hain agar khuda ki taraf se tum ko fatah miley to kehte hainkiya hum tumahray sath nah they. aur agar kafiroon ko ( fatah ) naseeb ho to ( un se ) kehte hainkiya hum tum par ghalib nahi they aur tum ko musalmanoon ( ke haath ) se bachaaya nahi. to khuda tum mein qayamat ke din faisla kardey ga. aur khuda kafiroon ko mominon par hargiz ghalba nahi day ga
  4,142,munhafiq ( un chalon se apne nazdeek ) khuda ko dhoka dete hain ( yeh is kokiya dhoka den ge ) woh inhen ko dhokay mein daalnay wala hai aur jab yeh namaz ko kharray hotay hain to sust aur kaahil ho kar ( sirf ) logon ke dikhaane ko aur khuda ki yaad hi nahi karte magar bohat kam
  4,143,beech mein parre latak rahay hain nah un ki taraf ( hotay hain ) nah un ki taraf aur jis ko khuda bhutkaye to is ke liye kabhi bhi rasta nah pao ge
  4,144,ae ahal imaan! mominon ke siwa kafiroon ko dost nah banaaokiya tum chahtay ho ke apne oopar khuda ka Sarih ilzaam lau ?
  4,145,kuch shak nahi ke munhafiq log dozakh ke sab se neechay ke darjay mein hon ge. aur tum un ka kisi ko madadgaar nah pao ge
  4,146,haan jinhon ne tauba ki aur apni haalat ko durustkiya aur khuda ( ki rassi ) ko mazboot pakra aur khaas khuda ke farmanbardar hogaye to aisay log mominon ke zamray mein hon ge aur khuda anqareeb mominon ko bara sawab day ga
  4,147,agar tum ( khuda ke shukar guzar raho aur ( is par ) imaan le aao to khuda tum ko azaab day karkiya kere ga. aur khuda to qadar shanas aur Dana hai
  4,148,khuda is baat ko pasand nahi karta ke koi kisi ko alania bura kahe magar woh jo mazloom ho. aur khuda ( sab kuch ) santa ( aur ) jaanta hai
  4,149,agar tum log bhalai khullam khula karo ge ya chhupa kar ya buraiee se dar guzar karo ge to khuda bhi maaf karne wala ( aur ) sahib qudrat hai
  4,150,jo log khuda se aur is ke payghambaroon se kufar karte hain aur khuda aur is ke payghambaroon mein farq karna chahtay hain aur kehte hain ke hum baaz ko mantay hain aur baaz ko nahi mantay aur imaan aur kufar ke beech mein aik raah nikalni chahtay hain
  4,151,woh bulaa ishtibaah kafir hain aur kafiroon ke liye hum ne zillat ka azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  4,152,aur jo log khuda aur is ke payghambaroon par imaan laaye aur un mein se kisi mein farq nahkiya ( yani sab ko maana ) aisay logon ko woh anqareeb un ( ki nakiyon ) ke siilay ataa farmaiye ga aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  4,153,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) ahal kitaab tum se darkhwast karte hain ke tum un par aik ( likhi hui ) kitaab aasman se utaar lao to yeh moose se is se bhi barri barri darkhwasten kar chukay hain ( un se ) kehte they hamein khuda zahir ( yani aankhon se ) dikha do so un ke gunah ki wajah se un ko bijli ne aapkrha. phir khuli nishanain aeye peechay bichhre ko ( mabood ) bana baithy to is se bhi hum ne dar guzar ki. aur moose ko Sarih ghalba diya
  4,154,aur un se ehad lainay ko hum ne un par koh tor utha kharakiya aur inhen hukum diya ke ( shehar ke ) darwazay mein ( daakhil hona to ) sajda karte hue daakhil hona aur yeh bhi hukum diya ke haftay ke din ( machhliyan pakarney ) mein tajaweez ( yani hukum ke khilaaf ) nah karna. gharz hum ne un se mazboot ehad liya
  4,155,( lekin unhon ne ehad ko toar dala ) to un ke ehad toar dainay aur khuda ki ayaton se kufar karne aur anbia ko na-haq maar daalnay aur yeh kehnay ke sabab ke hamaray dilon par parday ( parre hue ) hain. ( khuda ne un ko mardood kardiya aur un ke dilon par parday nahi hain ) balkay un ke kufar ke sabab khuda ne un par mohar kar di hai to yeh kam hi imaan laatay hain
  4,156,aur un ke kufar ke sabab aur maryam par aik bohtan azeem bandhnay ke sabab
  4,157,aur yeh kehnay ke sabab ke hum ne maryam ke betay eesa maseeh ko jo khuda ke paighambar ( kehlate ) they qatal kardiya hai ( khuda ne un ko ma'l-oon kardiya ) aur unhon ne eesa ko qatal nahikiya aur nah inhen suli par charhaya balkay un ko un ki si soorat maloom hui aur jo log un ke baray mein ikhtilaaf karte hain woh un ke haal se shak mein parre hue hain aur peroi-e- zan ke siwa un ko is ka mutlaq ilm nahi. aur unhon ne eesa ko yaqeenan qatal nahikiya
  4,158,balkay khuda ne un ko apni taraf utha liya. aur khuda ghalib aur hikmat wala hai
  4,159,aur koi ahal kitaab nahi hoga magar un ki mout se pehlay un par imaan le aeye ga. aur woh qayamat ke din un par gawah hon ge
  4,160,to hum ne yahudion ke zulmo ke sabab ( bohat si ) pakeeza cheezein jo un ko halal theen un par haraam kar dein aur is sabab se bhi ke woh aksar khuda ke raste se ( logon ko ) roktay they
  4,161,aur is sabab se bhi ke bawajood mana kiye jaane ke sood letay they aur is sabab se bhi ke logon ka maal na-haq khatay they. aur un mein se jo kafir hain un ke liye hum ne dard dainay wala azaab tayyar kar rakha hai
  4,162,magar jo log un mein se ilm mein pakkay hain aur jo momin hain woh is ( kitaab ) par jo tum par nazil hui aur jo ( kitaaben ) tum se pehlay nazil huien ( sab par ) imaan rakhtay hain aur namaz parhte hain aur zkat dete hain aur khuda aur roz akhirat ko mantay hain. un ko hum anqareeb ajar azeem den ge
  4,163,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam ) hum ne tumhari taraf isi terhan wahi bhaije hai jis terhan Nooh aur un se pichlle payghambaroon ki taraf bhaije thi. aur ibrahim aur asmayl aur Ishaq aur Yaqoob aur aulaad Yaqoob aur eesa aur ayub aur Younis aur Haroon aur Sulaiman ki taraf bhi hum ne wahi bhaije thi aur dawod ko hum ne Zaboor bhi inayat ki thi
  4,164,aur bohat se paighambar hain jin ke halaat hum tum se peshtar bayan kar chukay hain aur bohat se paighambar hain jin ke halaat tum se bayan nahi kiye. aur moose se to khuda ne baatein bhi kee
  4,165,( sab ) payghambaroon ko ( khuda ne ) khushkhabri sunanay walay aur darane walay ( bana kar bheja tha ) taakay payghambaroon ke anay ke baad logon ko khuda par ilzaam ka mauqa nah rahay aur khuda ghalib hikmat wala hai
  4,166,lekin khuda ne jo ( kitaab ) tum par nazil ki hai is ki nisbat khuda gawahi deta hai ke is ne apne ilm se nazil ki hai aur farishtay bhi gawahi dete hain. aur gawah to khuda hi kaafi hai
  4,167,jin logon ne kufarkiya aur ( logon ko ) khuda ke raste se roka woh raste se bhatak kar daur ja parre
  4,168,jo log kafir hue aur zulm karte rahay khuda un ko bakhsnay wala nahi aur nah inhen rasta hi dukhaay ga
  4,169,haan dozakh ka rasta jis mein woh hamesha ( jaltay ) rahen ge. aur yeh ( baat ) khuda ko aasaan hai
  4,170,logo! khuda ke paighambar tumahray paas tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se haq baat le kar aeye hain to ( un par ) imaan lao ( yahi ) tumahray haq mein behtar hai. aur agar kufar karo ge to ( jaan rakho ke ) jo kuch asmano aur zameen mein hai sab Kuda hi ka hai aur khuda sab kuch jan-nay wala ( aur ) hikmat wala hai
  4,171,ae ahal kitaab apne deen ( ki baat ) mein hadd se nah badho aur khuda ke baray mein haq ke siwa kuch nah kaho. maseeh ( yani ) maryam ke betay eesa ( nah khuda they nah khuda ke betay balkay ) khuda ke rasool aur ka kalma ( basharat ) they jo is ne maryam ki taraf bheja tha aur is ki taraf se aik rooh they to khuda aur iss ke rasoloo par imaan lao. aur ( yeh ) nah kaho ( ke khuda ) teen ( hain. is aitqaad se ) baz aao ke yeh tumahray haq mein behtar hai. khuda hi mabood wahid hai aur is se pak hai ke is ke aulaad ho. jo kuch asmano mein aur jo kuch zameen mein hai sab isi ka hai. aur khuda hi karsaaz kaafi hai
  4,172,maseeh is baat se aar nahi rakhtay ke khuda ke bande hon aur nah Maqarrab farishtay ( aar rakhtay hain ) aur jo shakhs khuda ka bandah honay ko mojab aar samjhay aur sar kashi kere to khuda sab ko apne paas jama karle ga
  4,173,to jo log imaan laaye aur naik kaam karte rahay woh un ko un ka poora badla day ga aur apne fazl se kuch ziyada bhi inayat kere ga. aur jinhon ne ( bundon honay se ) aaro inkaar aur taqqaburkiya un ko takleef dainay wala azaab day ga. aur yeh log khuda ke siwa apna haami aur madadgaar nah payen ge
  4,174,logo tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se tumahray paas Daleel ( roshan ) aa chuki hai aur hum ne ( kufar aur zilalat ka andhera daur karne ko ) tumhari taraf chamakta howa noor bhaij diya hai
  4,175,pas jo log khuda par imaan laaye aur is ( ke deen ki rassi ) ko mazboot pakdae rahay un ko woh apni rehmat aur fazl ( ke bahishtoon ) mein daakhil kere ga. aur apni taraf ( p_hchne ka ) seedha rasta dukhaay ga
  4,176,( ae paighambar ) log tum se ( kalalah ke baray mein ) hukum ( khuda ) daryaft karte hain keh do ke khuda kalalah ke baray mein yeh hukum deta hai ke agar koi aisa mard marjaye jis ke aulaad nah ho ( aur nah maa baap ) aur is ke behan ho to is ko bhai ke trke mein se aadha hissa miley ga. aur agar behan marjaye aur is ke aulaad nah ho to is ke tamam maal ka waris bhai hoga aur agar ( marnay walay bhai ki ) do behnain hon to dono ko bhai ke trke mein se do tahai. aur agar bhai aur behan yani mard aur aurtain miley jalay waris hon to mard ka hissa do aurton ke barabar hai. ( yeh ehkaam ) khuda tum se is liye bayan farmata hai ke bhataktay nah phiro. aur khuda har cheez se waaqif hai
